Maintainer: Maxime Haselbauer maxime.haselbauer@googlemail.com
Build-Depends: dpkg-dev (>= 1.18)

Package: cmake-dependency-diagram
Architecture: all
Depends: graphviz
Description: CMake dependency diagram generator
 This package provides a tool to generate dependency diagrams for CMake
 projects. It uses the CMake language server to extract the dependencies and
 Graphviz to create the diagrams.

 